guided generation. Potential impact spans high-stakes domains such as regulatory compliance, clinical decision support, and contract analysis, where understanding how multiple conditions interact—including when they are overridden—is critical. By integrating insights from semantic parsing, abductive reasoning, and differentiable program synthesis, TraceFormer represents a shift from reactive module triggering to proactive, learnable trace construction.",
