egal document analysis, medical guideline interpretation, and compliance checking, where precise handling of exceptions and conditional rules is essential. By integrating insights from natural logic (Paper 1), structured reasoning (Paper 2), and modular neural architectures (Paper 3), NLC advances beyond monolithic reasoning models toward truly composable, explainable AI.",
